# Holdings & avg_cost

## Average-cost method (required)
```javascript
// BUY: weighted average including fee
nextAvg = (prevShares * prevAvg + shares * price + fee) / nextShares
// SELL: reduce shares; avg per share unchanged until zero
```

## Forbidden
```javascript
// ❌ lifetime buy average — wrong after partial sells
avgCost = totalBuyCost / totalBuyShares
```

## Transaction order
```sql
ORDER BY date ASC, created_at ASC, id ASC
```
Use `fetchOrderedTransactions` pattern for validation; `syncHoldingFromTransactions` must match.

## Consistency
- `computePortfolioPnL` (frontend) and `positionsAtDate` (backend history) use the same logic
- `holding.avg_cost` in DB must match — run `rebuildHoldingsFromTransactions` after logic changes
